This is a cheat-proof data type with a sample program.

To use this data type, you need to include noCheat.h and copy the directory external. Then, replace:
int variableThatIsInterestingForCheaters;
with
NoCheat<int> variableThatIsInterestingForCheaters;
and you are done.

This package is released under BSD 2-clause license, which is available in LICENSE.txt
